occupationType1.name: Officer
occupationType1.description: Commissioned military class responsible for authority and command.

occupationType2.name: Engineer
occupationType2.description: Imperial engineers are the repairman units for the Empire.

occupationType3.name: Medical
occupationType3.description: A type of soldier and officer attached to the Galactic Empire's ground and naval forces that has specialized medical training.

occupationType4.name: Security
occupationType4.description: A law-enforcement and intelligence agency of the Galactic Empire charged with matters of internal state security and ensuring the loyalty of citizens.

occupationType5.name: Technician
occupationType5.description: Imperial weapons technicians, also known as Imperial gunners, operate turbolasers and ion cannons of capital ships and military bases.

occupationType6.name: Stormtrooper
occupationType6.description: Stormtroopers serve as frontline assault forces and form the backbone of the Imperial Military.
